				<wikidot:authorName>Alces_alces</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4057128</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I would like to give a thank you to all of the following people who helped make Craydaddy a thing, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/magnadeus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3499685&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1552051865" alt="magnadeus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3499685)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/magnadeus" >magnadeus</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/eskobar" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1173523&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1552051865" alt="Eskobar" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1173523)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/eskobar" >Eskobar</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaguebearer" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4364963&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1552051865" alt="plaguebearer" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4364963)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaguebearer" >plaguebearer</a></span>. A big Mcthankis from Mcspankies to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1552051865" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span> for helping with the picture and dialogue. Another thank you to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hotcoles" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3997195&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1552051865" alt="HotColes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3997195)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hotcoles" >HotColes</a></span> for allowing me to steal the lovely text coding you saw in this. ETA: Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ayers" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1856789&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1552051865" alt="Ayers" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1856789)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ayers" >Ayers</a></span> for shorting down the code so it didn't take up a literal 24 pages on google docs.</p> <p>This was originally meant to be about a rapping crayfish but, with some thought, I decided to change it. Though just for shits and giggles here was an excerpt from what I had.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Father&nbsp;crayfish&nbsp;vol.&nbsp;1</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-vol.&nbsp;2&nbsp;out&nbsp;soon</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <blockquote> <p>YO YO YO ITS YA BOI CRAYDADDY ON THE BEAT!<br /> HAVING A GOOD TIME DOWN HERE IN THE CREEK,<br /> DOIN MY THING TILL THIS CRAZY LIL SHIT CAME BY AND PICKED ME UP OFF MY FEET,<br /> NOW I GOTTA PUT OUT A HIT I AINT NO BITCH, THIS BITCH GOIN BE YEET.<br /> CLACK CLACK MOTHERFUCKER!<br /> WHOSE GOT YOU NOW!<br /> CLACK CLACK MOTHERFUCKER!<br /> WHOSE GOT YOU NOW!<br /> CLACK CLACK MOTHERFUCKER!<br /> YOU'LL BE CRYING 'OW'!</p> </blockquote> </div> </div> </div> <br /> If you want to see more of my stuff then check out my author page! <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/a-wild-alces-alces-is-plugging">Shameless plug</a>
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
